          "summary": "Shortbread Lemon Bars requires about <b>1 hour and 10 minutes</b> from start to finish. One portion of this dish contains around <b>4g of protein</b>, <b>9g of fat</b>, and a total of <b>248 calories</b>. This recipe serves 9 and costs 36 cents per serving. This recipe is liked by 186 foodies and cooks. It is a good option if you're following a <b>lacto ovo vegetarian</b> diet. A mixture of salt, butter, fat milk, and a handful of other ingredients are all it takes to make this recipe so tasty. It works well as a dessert. It is brought to you by Pick Fresh Foods. With a spoonacular <b>score of 14%</b>, this dish is rather bad. If you like this recipe, you might also like recipes such as <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/strawberry-lemon-shortbread-bars-130364\">Strawberry Lemon Shortbread Bars</a>, <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/strawberry-lemon-shortbread-bars-171931\">Strawberry Lemon Shortbread Bars</a>, and <a href=\"https://spoonacular.com/recipes/luscious-lemon-shortbread-bars-365704\">Luscious Lemon Shortbread Bars</a>.",
